The paper deals with image and video understanding using deep convolutional neural networks and support-vector-machines, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. The focus of the paper is on action recognition, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of deep neural networks, which is a popular topic in the field of neural networks (cs.NE).
